flowchart TB
    User[User or Professor]
    Browser[Browser]
    Frontend[Vue SPA<br/>Router · Pages · useStore<br/>PDF Viewer · Chat Q&A · Admin]
    Proxy[Nginx Reverse Proxy<br/>TLS · Security Headers · Gzip]
    RateLimit[slowapi Rate Limiter<br/>Auth 5/min · AI 10/min]
    Backend[FastAPI Backend<br/>REST API · OpenAPI · structlog]
    DB[(PostgreSQL<br/>Users · Documents · Jobs · Q&A)]
    Storage[(MinIO<br/>S3-Compatible Object Storage)]
    AI[AI Provider Chain<br/>Groq → Gemini → OpenAI → Fallback]
    Jobs[(Async Processing<br/>Background Tasks + Job Records)]
    Metrics[Prometheus Metrics<br/>/metrics]
    Observe[Grafana Dashboards]

    subgraph VPS[Hetzner VPS · Docker Compose]
        Proxy --> RateLimit
        RateLimit --> Backend
        Backend --> DB
        Backend --> Storage
        Backend --> AI
        Backend --> Jobs
